<div class="welcome-box">
  <!--===== 大图 =====-->
  <header id="header">
    <div class="header-wrapper-inner">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="welcome-speech">
          <h1>暴力入门，成为下一个想要的自己</h1>
          <p>Python 入门课，现已开放报名</p>
          <%= link_to('开始学习!', signup_path, class:'btn btn-push') %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro bg-light-gray">
    <div class="container"><!--左右两侧空白，替代方案是 div.col-md-offset-1 -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag("intro.jpg", class:"img-responsive center-block", alt:"intro") %><!--图片自适应，图片内容居中-->
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-7">
          <div class="intro-description">
            <h2>人人可学的教育平台</h2>
            <p>
              有学以认知心理学为基石，打破过去传统刻板的编程学习、培训途径，旨在为未来培养出一批能够快速贯通编程理念并灵活实践的全栈工程师。
            </p>

            <ul class="list-unstyled points">
              <li>
              <span>
                  <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
              </span>
                我们以班级为单位公布所有学员就业薪资
              </li>
              <li>
              <span>
                  <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
              </span>
                不标榜明星学员，因为人人都是就业明星
              </li>
              <li>
              <span>
                  <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
              </span>
                每入学10名学员，就有7名来自老学员推荐
              </li>
              <li>
              <span>
                  <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
              </span>
                不忘初心，向千万学子免费分享学习资源
              </li>
            </ul> <!-- end of /.points -->

            <a href="#" class="btn btn-black">
              教师团队
            </a> <!-- /purchase button -->
          </div> <!-- end of /.intro-description -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="feature-content text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon-box">
              <div class="feature-icon center-block">
                <i class="fa fa-laptop"></i>
              </div>
            </div> <!--  end of /.feature-icon-box  -->
            <div class="feature-info">
              <h3 class="feature-heading">课程免费学</h3>
              <p class="feature-description">
                有学致力于为未来培养出更多优秀的全栈工程师，我们已将价值万元的 VIP 付费课程全部免费开放。
              </p>  <!--   end of /.feature-description  -->
            </div> <!--   end of /.feature-info  -->
          </div> <!--  end of /.feature-content  -->
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="feature-content text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon-box">
              <div class="feature-icon center-block">
                <i class="fa fa-eye"></i>
              </div>
            </div> <!--  end of /.feature-icon-box  -->
            <div class="feature-info">
              <h3 class="feature-heading">教材简明易懂</h3>
              <p class="feature-description">
                专业术语太多？全英文看不懂？我们总结多年的线下教育经验编写了通俗易懂的教材，帮你降低学习门槛。
              </p>  <!--   end of /.feature-description  -->
            </div> <!--   end of /.feature-info  -->
          </div> <!--  end of /.feature-content  -->
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="feature-content text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon-box">
              <div class="feature-icon center-block">
                <i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>
              </div>
            </div> <!--  end of /.feature-icon-box  -->
            <div class="feature-info">
              <h3 class="feature-heading">业界大神倾心分享</h3>
              <p class="feature-description">
                大神与你分享十年敏捷开发、团队合作、项目管理经验，让你体验持续高速成长的乐趣。
              </p>  <!--   end of /.feature-description  -->
            </div> <!--   end of /.feature-info  -->
          </div> <!--  end of /.feature-content  -->
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="feature-content text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon-box">
              <div class="feature-icon center-block">
                <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
              </div>
            </div> <!--  end of /.feature-icon-box  -->
            <div class="feature-info">
              <h3 class="feature-heading">免费公开课直播</h3>
              <p class="feature-description">
                视频教程已发布10余万小时，累计下载量3200余万次，听课人数近百万人。
              </p>  <!--   end of /.feature-description  -->
            </div> <!--   end of /.feature-info  -->
          </div> <!--  end of /.feature-content  -->
        </div>

      </div>
    </div> <!-- end of /.container -->
  </section>

  <!--===== 服务优势 =====-->
  <section class="service-box">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <h2>服务优势</h2> <!-- 副标题 -->
        <div class="short-line"></div> <!-- 分隔线 -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <div class="box">
              <%= image_tag("jimi/service_1.png") %> <!-- 图示 -->
              <h3>品质保证</h3> <!-- 标题 -->
              <p>本店的商品皆通过市场验证，使用最高级的材料制作而成，品质为业界领先标准。</p> <!-- 内文 -->
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <div class="box">
              <%= image_tag("jimi/service_2.png") %>
              <h3>快速送达</h3>
              <p>全国皆享有当天下单、隔日送达的服务，过程中有任何损坏皆由我们负责，请放心购买。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <div class="box">
              <%= image_tag("jimi/service_3.png") %>
              <h3>安心使用</h3>
              <p>设计皆考量人体工学及真实使用情境，使用起来更安心。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--===== 推荐商品 =====-->
  <section class="show-box">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <h2>推荐商品</h2> <!-- 副标题 -->
        <div class="short-line"></div> <!-- 分隔线 -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= link_to '#' do %> <!-- 商品连结 -->
              <div class="box"><%= image_tag("home/java.jpg") %></div> <!-- 商品图片 -->
              <div class="content">
                <p>两手锅</p> <!-- 商品名称 -->
                <p>$550</p> <!-- 商品价格 -->
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= link_to '#' do %>
              <div class="box"><%= image_tag("home/python.jpg") %></div>
              <div class="content">
                <p>平底锅</p>
                <p>$750</p>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= link_to '#' do %>
              <div class="box"><%= image_tag("home/javascript.jpg") %></div>
              <div class="content">
                <p>铁制茶壶</p>
                <p>$450</p>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= link_to '#' do %>
              <div class="box"><%= image_tag("home/java.jpg") %></div>
              <div class="content">
                <p>茶壶</p>
                <p>$250</p>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--===== 用户反馈 =====-->
  <section class="feedback-box">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <h2>用户反馈</h2> <!-- 副标题 -->
        <div class="short-line"></div> <!-- 分隔线 -->
        <div id="feedback" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!--===== 轮播按钮 =====-->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#feedback" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#feedback" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#feedback" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>

          <!--===== 轮播内容 =====-->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
              <p>这是我用过最好的网站，商品众多、下单方便、送货快速，还能订制特殊规格的锅具，强力推荐。</p>
              <%= image_tag("avatar/a4.png") %> <!-- 图片 -->
              <strong>Eddie - 上班族</strong> <!-- 介绍 -->
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <p>我是这网站的忠实用户，已经在这买好几年了，质量一直很好，而且不定时会有折扣，真的很划算！</p>
              <%= image_tag("avatar/a1.png") %>
              <strong>Anna - 家庭主妇</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <p>身为一个学生，预算不太多，却也能在这找到便宜又有设计感的器皿，让我生活又添加一份乐趣。</p>
              <%= image_tag("avatar/a6.png") %>
              <strong>Kobe - 大学生</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--===== 合作品牌 =====-->
  <section class="brand-box bg-light-gray">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <h2>合作品牌</h2>
        <div class="short-line"></div>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_1.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_2.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_3.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_4.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_5.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_6.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_7.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_8.png") %>
        <%= image_tag("jimi/brand_9.png") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--===== 立即购买 =====-->
  <section class="push-box">
    <%= link_to('开始学习!', '#', class:'btn btn-push') %>
  </section>
</div>